data.description: Seller is packed and ready to move. Bring offers on this 2 bedroom 2 bath Delphina villa in Crescent Ridge in On Top of the world. Spacious and open split floor plan. Covered porch leads to leaded glass front door to Living room. This home has an large kitchen with breakfast nook. sliding doors open to a screened in lanai and rear patio.  Master Bedroom has ensuite bath with walk in shower and walk in closet. Guest bedroom could be used as an office or for your guests. 2nd bath has tub/shower combination. Lots of ceiling fans to help make home very comfortable along with shade from trees in front and back yard  Vinyl plank flooring in living areas and ceramic tile in master with carpet in  guest bedroom. Roof -2012. HVAC -2010. Hot Water heater - 2018  Microwave, dishwasher ,garbage disposal -2020.   Recreation center located just 1/2 mile away where you can  enjoy pool, pickle ball, Raquet ball, . There is a gym, pub, hobby building and softball field. Lots of other activities are also offered. HOA offers Maintenance free living including lawn care, Ext maintenance, internet cable and 24 hour manned gates. Lot to enjoy at On Top of the World
